@model JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Common.Pagination.PagedResult<JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Templates.MessageTemplateSummary>
@inject JioCxRcsWrapper.Web.Services.PermissionUiService PermissionUi
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Message Builder";
    var canAdd = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("MessageBuilder", "Add");
    var canUpdate = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("MessageBuilder", "Update");
    var canDelete = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("MessageBuilder", "Delete");
}

<section class="page-hero panel-hero">
    <div>
        <div class="page-eyebrow">Template Studio</div>
        <h1>Message Builder</h1>
        <p>Create and manage send-ready RCSX templates with media uploaded to JioCX.</p>
    </div>
    @if (canAdd)
    {
        <a asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-primary panel-primary-btn">Create Template</a>
    }
</section>

<section class="metric-strip">
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Templates</span><strong>@ViewBag.TemplateCount</strong></article>
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Rich Cards</span><strong>@ViewBag.RichCards</strong></article>
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Media Ready</span><strong>@ViewBag.MediaReady</strong></article>
</section>

@if (TempData["SuccessMessage"] is string successMessage)
{
    <div class="alert alert-success">@successMessage</div>
}
@if (TempData["ErrorMessage"] is string errorMessage)
{
    <div class="alert alert-danger">@errorMessage</div>
}

<section class="panel-card mb-4">
    <div class="panel-card-header">
        <div>
            <h2>Filters</h2>
            <p>Filter templates by name, type, or client.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label">Template Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="Name" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["Name"]" placeholder="Filter by name..." />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label">Message Type</label>
                <select class="form-select form-select-sm grid-filter-select" data-column="Type">
                    <option value="">All Types</option>
                    @foreach (var type in Enum.GetValues<JioCxRcsWrapper.Domain.Enums.MessageType>())
                    {
                        <option value="@type" selected="@(ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["Type"] == type.ToString())">@type</option>
                    }
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label">Client Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="ClientName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["ClientName"]" placeholder="Filter by client..." />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="panel-card">
    <div class="panel-card-header">
        <div>
            <h2>Template Library</h2>
            <p>Stored payloads are ready for Send Message API usage.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table panel-table align-middle mb-0">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Name</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Client</th>
                <th>Preview</th>
                <th class="text-end action-cell">Actions</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            @foreach (var template in Model.Items)
            {
                var previewUrl = !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(template.LocalMediaPath) 
                    ? template.LocalMediaPath 
                    : template.RcsMediaUrl;
                <tr>
                    <td class="fw-semibold">@template.Name</td>
                    <td><span class="status-pill status-scheduled">@template.MessageType</span></td>
                    <td>@template.ClientName</td>
                    <td>
                        @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(previewUrl))
                        {
                            <a href="@previewUrl" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info" title="Preview Media">
                                <i class="bi bi-eye"></i>
                            </a>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <span class="text-muted small">No Media</span>
                        }
                    </td>
                    <td class="text-end action-cell">
                        <div class="action-stack">
                        @if (canUpdate)
                        {
                            <a asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@template.Id" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Update</a>
                        }
                        @if (canDelete)
                        {
                            <form asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@template.Id" method="post" class="d-inline" onsubmit="return confirm('Delete this template?');">
                                @Html.AntiForgeryToken()
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger">Delete</button>
                            </form>
                        }
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <partial name="_Pager" model="Model" />
</section>
